---
import imgProgram from "@images/blue-skies-auburn-university-student-pilot-programs.webp"
---
<section class="flex flex-col items-center">
  <div class="max-w-4xl flex flex-col py-10 px-5">
    <h3 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold">Discover Our Leaseback Program</h3>
    <h4 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 py-5">Invest in an Aircraft and Earn Income</h4>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Blue Skies Aboveâ€™s Leaseback Program offers a unique investment opportunity, allowing you to own an aircraft while generating rental income. Based at Lanett Regional Airport, our program provides the chance to offset ownership costs while contributing to the training of future pilots.</p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 pt-10">
      By partnering with Blue Skies Above, you can enjoy the benefits of aircraft ownership with the added advantage of rental revenue. We offer flexible options and professional support for managing your aircraft within our training fleet at Lanett Regional Airport.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-gradient-to-l from-slate-200 to-blue-50 py-14" id="contact">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-center">Join the Blue Skies Above Leaseback Program</h1>
  <div class="lg:flex lg:flex-row-reverse items-center">

    <div class="mx-10 lg:px-16 lg:w-1/2">
      <form class="contents" action="/leaseback_programs" accept-charset="UTF-8" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value="3O-5UiAB4xUSXET4JnwO3jneQEttrj6T9NaYpM5h090oTv1hdbHNYpUbrqpnfkeBKqKSePlo7PewCKP9fH4grQ" autocomplete="off">

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_name">Name</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[name]" id="leaseback_program_name">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_email">Email</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[email]" id="leaseback_program_email">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_phone">Phone</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[phone]" id="leaseback_program_phone">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_aircraft_manufacturer">Aircraft manufacturer</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[aircraft_manufacturer]" id="leaseback_program_aircraft_manufacturer">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_aircraft_model">Aircraft model</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[aircraft_model]" id="leaseback_program_aircraft_model">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_aircraft_year">Aircraft year</label>
    <input class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" type="text" name="leaseback_program[aircraft_year]" id="leaseback_program_aircraft_year">
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <label for="leaseback_program_message">Message</label>
    <textarea rows="4" class="block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-400 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-full" name="leaseback_program[message]" id="leaseback_program_message"></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="inline">
    <input type="submit" name="commit" value="APPLY" class="btn-primary mb-10 lg:mb-0" data-disable-with="APPLY">
  </div>
</form>   
    </div>

    <div class="mx-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <img class="lg:pb-10 lg:pt-5 lg:pl-5" alt="Blue Skies Pair of Cessnas at Lannet Municipal Airport" src={imgProgram.src}>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>